    {
      "id": "E:note:row528894:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "51 yo M admitted to [**Hospital1 **] for altered MS(his sister found him earlier",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row528894#s1",
      "text": "51 yo M admitted to [**Hospital1 **] for altered MS(his sister found him earlier    on [**2-14**] lethargic and she brought him to ED)He had a CT which showed    SAH.He was transfered to [**Hospital1 **].In ED he was intubated for altered MS.Pt in    DIC and CT of head and torso showed stable SAh and multiple septic    emboli and infarcts to kidneys and spleen.In sepsis with lactate of 14    at OSH down to 9.6 here.Pt transferred to MICU for further management."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row528894:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Subarachnoid hemorrhage (SAH)    Assessment:    Pt with SAH.Rd the pt from ED se",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row528894#s2",
      "text": "Subarachnoid hemorrhage (SAH)    Assessment:    Pt with SAH.Rd the pt from ED sedated on propofol.CT in ED with stable    bleed with not change from the one done from the OSH."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row528894:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Action:    Neurosurg following.Q 1hr neuro obs stable.Remains sedated on propofo",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row528894#s3",
      "text": "Action:    Neurosurg following.Q 1hr neuro obs stable.Remains sedated on propofol    for pt comfort."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row528894:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Response:    Neuro exam unchanged.Pt localizes to nailbed stimuli.PEARL size 2.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row528894#s4",
      "text": "Response:    Neuro exam unchanged.Pt localizes to nailbed stimuli.PEARL size 2."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row528894:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Plan:    Cont Q 1hr neuro checks.CT head in am.Keep INR <1.4 and plts >50 as per",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row528894#s5",
      "text": "Plan:    Cont Q 1hr neuro checks.CT head in am.Keep INR <1.4 and plts >50 as per    neurosurgery recs."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row528894:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Respiratory failure, acute (not ARDS/[**Doctor Last Name 11**])    Assessment:  ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row528894#s6",
      "text": "Respiratory failure, acute (not ARDS/[**Doctor Last Name 11**])    Assessment:    Pt was intubated in ED for acute MS changes.Rd the pt on AC 50%/PEEP    5/TV 530/RR 16.Pt overbreathing on the vent.LS clear."
    },
    {
